node.text:
Rainbow ballet 🌈 🐦 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on worlderlust.com (link in my bio: @worlderlust)

These photos of the black & white jacobin hummingbird capture the exact moment in which the sunlight penetrates the wings of a Black and white Jacobin hummingbird revealing a secret of nature that cannot be seen with our eyes. These photos contain no digital manipulation.

📷 @christianspencerphoto

node.text:
Umbrella tree 🌳 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on worlderlust.com (link in my bio: @worlderlust)

How impressive is this holm oak? Known as the umbrella tree. Once a year two gardeners climb up into its crown on ladders, and for two weeks they prune the tree like a skirt as they meticulously trim it into shape. Its healing powers helped James Bond recuperate – Casino Royale.

📽 @brigrc
📍Villa del Balbianello, Como, Italy
